# ── Graphify scope: CODE WIRING ONLY ──────────────────────────────────────
# Separation of concerns: your INTENT (markdown, specs, journal, custom skills)
# stays out of the graph. Graphify indexes only code structure — the AST wiring
# (imports, call graphs, classes, functions). gitignore syntax; ! negation works.
# NOTE: when a .graphifyignore is present, graphify uses it instead of falling
# back to .gitignore, so we re-declare deps/build/artifacts here explicitly.

# ── Intent & documentation (the markdown-based pipeline) ───────────────────
*.md
*.mdx
docs/
journal/
blog/
research/
inbox/
skills/        # custom Claude skills — intent, not wiring
.claude/
.remember/
.pi/
.github/

# ── Dependencies, build output, generated ─────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
graphify-out/
package-lock.json

# ── Binaries & media (never useful to the graph) ──────────────────────────
*.mp4
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.pdf
*.webm
*.zip
